</code></pre></div></div>

<p>We got a shell with low privileges.</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>root@kali:~/VulnOS2<span class="nv">$ </span>nc <span class="nt">-vlnp</span> 443
